Hangover is the new single from Taio Cruz ft Flo Rida taken from the brand new forthcoming album TY.O on Mercury Records / Universal.

Hardwell added his magic touch on the remix with stabby synths and a destroying bassline! Staying close to the original but making it a perfect match for the weekends and a sure party starter! The original radio version is taking the World by storm and will hit the top of the charts in no time! The official video has over 5,5 million views in just one week! Check out this new party anthem! 

Release TBC (Hardwell Instrumental Mix will be included in the package)

description:
DUTCH AND PIANO MAKE "DUTCHANO"! SOON ON MIXMASH.

Avesta, who recently released his remix on Revero's You Are Mine, is now back on Mixmash and this time not alone. Together with his Swiss colleague B Valley he worked out a true banger: adding epic piano chords, smashing it with crazy build-ups and pushing the famous Dutch sound to the limit! Since the words like "piano" and "Dutch" became the driving force of the track, the original "Dutchano" name was born.
"Dutchano" has this powerful festival anthem sound, and that was a reason none other than Laidback Luke picked up the tune for his own edit. We guarantee you falling in love with this one and begging for more of "Dutchano".

See this ultimate release available on Beatport from the 17th of November already!
title: Avesta & B Valley - Dutchano (Laidback Luke Edit)
